  <description><![CDATA[<p>Merligen lies on the serene <a data-udi="umb://document/7d838fa65a44467f9a85c30c8d2de877" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d838fa65a44467f9a85c30c8d2de877}" title="Lake Thun">Lake Thun</a>, with the old town of Thun and its proud castle at one end, and Interlaken, with its glorious views of the Jungfrau, at the other. Lake steamers stopping close to the Hotel Beatus regularly visit all the charming lakeside villages, and provide a delightful way of exploring the area. Alternatively, a regular bus service links the lake resorts with Thun and Interlaken in just 30 minutes. Merligen is a peaceful village, with just a few shops and cafés. Gentle lakeside walks are well signposted, and further well-trodden paths take in sights such as the vineyards and castle at Oberhofen, and the picturesque villages of Faulensee and Beatenberg. Guests will be overwhelmed by the choice of day excursions: there is plenty to explore. See <a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a> for full details and for multi-centre options.</p>
<p>In Merligen you'll have a telephone service - if you want to know more about the area or have any queries give us a call.</p>]]></description>
