  <excursions><![CDATA[<h3>Pre-Bookable</h3>
<p><strong>Day on Lake Thun and Lake Brienz</strong></p>
<p>From £28 (2nd class), £41 (1st class), daily<br />Spend a day cruising on the Lake Brienz, hopping on and off as you wish. Train to Brienz approx. Sfr5 return (pay locally).</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Jungfraujoch - Top of Europe*</strong></p>
<p>From £85, daily</p>
<p>A ‘must-see’ for all visitors is the ultimate rail journey through the Eiger, and up to Europe’s highest railway station at 3,454m, for breathtaking views including the 14km-long Aletsch glacier and the ‘Ice Palace'.</p>
<p>Many more options available locally through your Representative including</p>
<p><strong>Swiss Food and Culture Tour</strong> - from only Sfr20 per person - Exclusive to Inghams (book locally)</p>
<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at time of publishing but may vary up or down; correct prices will be advised at the time of booking</strong><em>.</em></p>]]></excursions>
